Brian A: The wheels, because they are always tired! Q: What did the stamp say to the envelope?
//*[contains(@aria-label, "Type a message")]//*[contains(@aria-label, "Type a message")]//*[contains(@aria-label, "Type A: An Avon lady at the North Pole!a message")]//*[contains(@aria-label, "Type a message")] Q: We're you long in the hospital? Q: What is it that even the most careful person overlooks? A: Her nose! Q: Which hand is it better to write with? A: Neither, it's best to write with a pen!

Brian
Q: Why did the man run around his bed?
A: To catch up on his sleep!

Brian
Q: What has four wheels and flies?
A: A garbage truck!
I'm thankful for friends like you guys!
